      "text": "펭귄"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.39,
      "end": 181.05,
      "text": "펭귄"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.05,
      "end": 181.29,
      "text": "펭귄"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.29,
      "end": 182.15,
      "text": "펭귄"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.15,
      "end": 182.85,
      "text": "아주 그냥"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.85,
      "end": 183.65,
      "text": "다이빙할 때만"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.65,
      "end": 184.31,
      "text": "나는 정도"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.31,
      "end": 185.45,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.45,
      "end": 186.15,
      "text": "그죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.15,
      "end": 186.87,
      "text": "물속으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.87,
      "end": 188.85,
      "text": "아무리 이렇게 새들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.85,
      "end": 190.13,
      "text": "훈련을 잘 받았다고"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.13,
      "end": 190.85,
      "text": "할지라도"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.85,
      "end": 192.33,
      "text": "저는 약간"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.33,
      "end": 193.17,
      "text": "걱정이 됐던 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.17,
      "end": 194.03,
      "text": "What if they suddenly"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.03,
      "end": 195.25,
      "text": "fly away"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.25,
      "end": 196.77,
      "text": "while filming it"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.77,
      "end": 197.13,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.13,
      "end": 197.83,
      "text": "Well"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.83,
      "end": 199.15,
      "text": "maybe that's their instinct"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.15,
      "end": 200.31,
      "text": "So I think"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.31,
      "end": 201.33,
      "text": "they should let them go"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.33,
      "end": 201.69,
      "text": "오"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.69,
      "end": 202.29,
      "text": "진짜요"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.29,
      "end": 203.59,
      "text": "If they want to fly away"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.59,
      "end": 203.89,
      "text": "어머"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.89,
      "end": 204.93,
      "text": "그냥 냅둬"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.93,
      "end": 205.39,
      "text": "그래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.39,
      "end": 206.43,
      "text": "Let them fly away"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.43,
      "end": 207.89,
      "text": "그러면 어떻게 또 영화를"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.89,
      "end": 208.99,
      "text": "계속해서 찍을까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.99,
      "end": 210.19,
      "text": "새로 캐스팅 해가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.19,
      "end": 211.83,
      "text": "I mean there are many"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.83,
      "end": 212.83,
      "text": "penguins in the area"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.83,
      "end": 213.91,
      "text": "penguins 말고"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.91,
      "end": 215.33,
      "text": "pelicans in the area"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.33,
      "end": 215.99,
      "text": "아니면"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.99,
      "end": 216.65,
      "text": "펭귄으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.65,
      "end": 217.55,
      "text": "가르다거나"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.55,
      "end": 219.07,
      "text": "penguins can't fly"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.07,
      "end": 220.95,
      "text": "못 나는 새로"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.95,
      "end": 222.59,
      "text": "저는 중간에 또"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.59,
      "end": 223.65,
      "text": "빵 터질 뻔 했잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.65,
      "end": 224.49,
      "text": "펭귄이 가고"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.49,
      "end": 225.01,
      "text": "펭귄으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.01,
      "end": 225.85,
      "text": "바뀌는 건가"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.85,
      "end": 227.71,
      "text": "I mean they can't fly away"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.71,
      "end": 228.35,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.35,
      "end": 229.51,
      "text": "But actually there was"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.51,
      "end": 230.63,
      "text": "a special technique"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.63,
      "end": 232.19,
      "text": "that was used"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.19,
      "end": 232.57,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.89,
      "end": 233.73,
      "text": "So the penguin"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.73,
      "end": 234.15,
      "text": "아"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.15,
      "end": 234.85,
      "text": "펭귄 왜 자꾸"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.85,
      "end": 235.53,
      "text": "펭귄이라고 하지"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.53,
      "end": 236.99,
      "text": "The pelican trainer"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.99,
      "end": 237.01,
      "text": "신이나"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.01,
      "end": 238.11,
      "text": "화가 나"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.11,
      "end": 238.93,
      "text": "아"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.93,
      "end": 239.53,
      "text": "펭귄 너무 좋아"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.53,
      "end": 240.29,
      "text": "저도요"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.29,
      "end": 241.41,
      "text": "The pelican trainer"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.41,
      "end": 242.65,
      "text": "he used"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.65,
      "end": 243.93,
      "text": "a red bucket"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.93,
      "end": 246.21,
      "text": "and this red bucket"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.21,
      "end": 247.33,
      "text": "meant food"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.33,
      "end": 248.19,
      "text": "밥"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.19,
      "end": 249.73,
      "text": "or specifically fish"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.73,
      "end": 250.33,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.33,
      "end": 251.05,
      "text": "If they saw"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.05,
      "end": 251.81,
      "text": "the red bucket"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.81,
      "end": 253.59,
      "text": "they were expecting"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.59,
      "end": 255.45,
      "text": "to get two whole fish"
    },
    {
